Parameters:
dodsName - the name for this dataset used by DODS
sourceFile - the source file name for this dataset
variables - the specified output variables
format - the format of the source file
title - title for this dataset
docURL - document URL for this dataset
userDAS - a local DAS file provided by user for this dataset
environment - environment variables used for this dataset
workDir - the working directory for Ferret when using this dataset
